definitions.definition: Full of lumps , not smooth , uneven .
examples: I don't know which was worse, the lumpy soup or the lumpy bed.

definitions.definition: Of a water surface: covered in many small waves as a result of wind; choppy .

main_definition: Full of lumps , not smooth , uneven .
